        <description>The third and final installment (after &lt;a href="/search/quick?game=Spy+vs%2e+Spy"&gt;Spy vs. Spy&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="/game/spy-vs-spy-the-island-caper"&gt;Spy vs. Spy: The Island Caper&lt;/a&gt;) sees the spies on an iceberg. They're seeking items (gyroscope, fuel canister, key card) and then seeking to leave via a rocket-ship before a blizzard sets in.  New trap items include a saw (for cutting holes in ice), a plunger detonator (with dynamite), an ice pick and snowshoes.  There are some pitfalls (thin ice and snow drifts).  Hand-to-hand combat is done with snowballs.  Watch your spy's body heat or he'll become a permanent resident.</description>
